Ek unique warm salad with a protein twist 😉

Straight from @shubham_vishwakkarma’s kitchen, build your bowl of salad that hits your protein intake in the yummiest possible way 🤤 

Ingredients 👇🏻

Vegetables: Yellow Zucchini, Broccoli, Red-Yellow and Green Capsicum, Beans, Cherry Tomatoes, Carrot, Lettuce, Olives, Sundried Tomatoes. 

Protein: 3 eggs (for non vegetarian diet) OR Chickpeas, Rajma (for vegetarian diet) 

Others: Garlic, Parsley, Olive Oil, Butter, Fresh Herbs, Dry Herbs, Chilli Flakes, Oregano, Salt, Goat Cheese. 

Try this at home and tag us in your stories 💪🏻 #EatWithHRX

6 simple ingredients 👇🏻
•Beetroot
•Nuts
